@startuml
initial state : Waiting for a new sale

state Waiting for a new sale {} : 
    -> Adding items one by one as they are selected by the customer : New item added

state Adding items one by one as they are selected by the customer {} : 
    -> Payment after all items have been added : All items added

state Payment after all items have been added {} : 
    --> Payment completed if paid in cash : Paid in cash
    --> Proceed to verify payment : Choose card or check

state Verify payment {} : 
    --> Payment approved : Payment verified

state Payment approved {} : 
    -> Sale completed : Sale finished

final state : Sale completed
@enduml
